    "Our goal with this library has been to provide a strong foundation upon which new features and additional functionality can be easily built, and we anticipate extending functionality to include GNNs in a future update.",
    "ConclusionsSlideflow is a flexible, end-to-end deep learning toolkit for digital pathology with computationally efficient whole-slide image processing, data storage cross-compatible with Tensorflow and PyTorch, efficient GPU-accelerated stain normalization, and a GUI to support deployment of trained deep learning models.",
    "Slideflow includes a variety of digital pathology deep learning methods to support a wide range of research objectives without switching software environments or reprocessing data.",
